requests.postData:
{"query":"
      query SearchRecommended {
        searchRecommendations {
          results {
            __typename
            ... on AppResult {
              id
              category
              title
              imageUrl
              score
              networks
              appId
              name
            }
            ... on BaseTokenResult {
              id
              category
              title
              imageUrl
              score
              symbol
              name
              coingeckoId
              marketCap
              verified
              perNetworkInfo {
                address
                network
              }
            }
            ... on DAOResult {
              id
              category
              title
              slug
              imageUrl
              score
              treasuryAddresses
              tokenAddress
              tags
            }
            ... on NftCollectionResult {
              id
              category
              title
              imageUrl
              score
              network
              address
              name
              monthlyVolume
              openseaSlug
              nftStandard
            }
            ... on UserResult {
              id
              category
              title
              imageUrl
              score
              address
              ens
            }
          }
        }
      }
    "}
